x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/oasis-1993@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">Noel Gallagher</a>公开了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>之前闻所未闻的“Definitely Maybe”早期录音——了解更多信息如下。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/every-oasis-song-ranked-greatness-best-worst-2488711">大师列表 - Oasis 录制的每首歌曲均按伟大程度排列</a></strong></li></ul><p>该乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-tease-reunion-announcement-after-liam-gallaghers-reading-2024-set-3787128">目前正在预告一些事情</a>，粉丝们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-fans-react-to-reunion-tease-one-of-the-most-culturally-significant-events-in-british-history-3787151">认为这将是一次重聚巡演</a>公告， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-30th-anniversary-reissue-of-definitely-maybe-featuring-unheard-versions-3758723">他们将于本周五 8 月 30 日发行“Definitely Maybe”30 周年纪念重新发行的早期唱片</a>。</p><p>这些录音（30 年前失踪）来自 Oasis 作为签约乐队的首次录音室录音。在磁带丢失之前，他们在南威尔士的蒙诺谷录音室录制了八首歌曲，最近终于被找回。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c134n75xm17o" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC</em></a>报道，诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 谈到丢失的录音时说道：“我一直说它们不可能失踪，这些录音带一定在某个地方。这些磁带被送到我们的唱片公司后就再也没有出现过。它是罐装的。结果发现它被贴错标签了。所以直到六个月前我才听说过 Monnow Valley 的唱片。” </p><figure id="attachment_3783517" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3783517" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3783517" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher.jpg" alt="绿洲乐队的利亚姆·加拉格尔和诺埃尔·加拉格尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OasisSad-Song-rare-demo-version-Liam-Gallagher-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3783517" class="wp-caption-text">绿洲乐队的利亚姆和诺埃尔·加拉格尔。图片来源：凯文·康明斯</figcaption></figure><p>在原始录音丢失后，Oasis 重新录制了这些歌曲并重新混音，最终以“Definitely Maybe”的形式发行。</p><p>周五发布的前所未闻的“失落曲目”包括“Live Forever”、“Cigarettes＆Alcohol”、“Rock &#39;n&#39; Roll Star”、“Shakermaker”和“Columbia”的早期版本。</p><p> 《Definitely Maybe》30 周年纪念版重新发行之际，Oasis 正在本周晚些时候发布一项公告——粉丝们相信这将是一次重聚巡演的公告。昨晚在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024">雷丁</a>节上，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher)</a>在演出即将结束时在屏幕上调侃了一次神秘约会，据称在“27.08.24”早上 8 点发布了一些消息。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blossoms">Blossoms</a>返校演出之后，同样的图片出现在曼彻斯特， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-tease-reunion-announcement-after-liam-gallaghers-reading-2024-set-3787128">以及演出结束后 Noel、Liam 和 Oasis 的官方 Twitter/X 上</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3776490" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3776490" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3776490" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Noel-and-Liam-Gallagher-posing.jpg" alt="Q 奖 Liam Gallagher 和 Noel Gallagher 与 OASIS、Noel Gallagher、Liam Gallagher 合影（摄影：Mick Hutson/Redferns）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Noel-and-Liam-Gallagher-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-