508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Van-McCann-of-Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-performs-live-on-stage-during-day-three-of-Reading-Festival-2024-at-Richfield-Avenue-on-August-25-2024-in-Reading-England.-Credit_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Van-McCann-of-Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-performs-live-on-stage-during-day-three-of-Reading-Festival-2024-at-Richfield-Avenue-on-August-25-2024-in-Reading-England.-Credit_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Van-McCann-of-Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-performs-live-on-stage-during-day-three-of-Reading-Festival-2024-at-Richfield-Avenue-on-August-25-2024-in-Reading-England.-Credit_-Simone-Joyner_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/catfish-and-the-bottlemen">Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen</a>成为今晚（8 月 25 日）<a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024">雷丁节</a>的头条新闻——以下是他们演奏的全部内容。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-liveblog-news-updates-reviews-rumours-photo-video-3785825">Reading &amp; Leeds 2024 直播博客：所有发生的动作</a></strong></li></ul><p>这是威尔士乐队第二次成为音乐节的主角。今晚备受期待的表演是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/leeds-festival-2024-heres-what-catfish-the-bottlemen-played-3786661">在周五（8 月 23 日）在利兹举行的比赛</a>之后进行的，尽管<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/leeds-festival-2024-extreme-weather-shuts-down-bbc-radio-1-and-aux-stage-3786214">风暴莉莉安对阵容中的其他地方造成了严重破坏，但比赛还是</a>顺利进行。</p><p>然而这一次，他们就没那么幸运了。事情一开始很顺利，范·麦肯 (Van McCann) 和他的同事伴随着<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队 (The Beatles)</a>的《Helter Skelter》进入主舞台，然后开始演奏他们 2019 年专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-the-balance-review-2480270#:~:text=There%20are%20solid%20pop%2Drock,had%20a%20one%2Doff%20tune.">The Balance</a> 》中的《Longshot》。</p><p>然而，到了第二首歌时，乐队在“凯瑟琳”期间遇到了一些技术困难。这意味着这首歌和他们的演出最终被缩短了。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">鲶鱼阅读时的力量被切断了 naahhhh</p><p> - 哎呀（@georgtiia） <a href="https://twitter.com/georgtiia/status/1827784720106549739?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024年8月25日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">鲶鱼演奏了一首半歌曲，然后被打断，读到 1-0 贝拉</p><p>— 铃<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f514.png" alt="🔔" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> (@isabellaliily) <a href="https://twitter.com/isabellaliily/status/1827785773279551696?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 8 月 25 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>他们休息了 15 分钟后回来，麦肯说：“你现在能听到我们说话吗？我们不需要吉他之类的”，然后恰如其分地突然响起“Soundcheck”。</p><div class="playlist-player-container"><p>在其他地方，还有对威尔士乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stereophonics">Stereophonics</a>厚颜无耻的简短致敬，他们在《辐射》的片尾曲中演奏了一段《调酒师与小偷》的片段。充气鳄鱼也一度被释放到人群中。</p><p>乐队一边演奏着三张专辑中的热门歌曲，一边向人群释放充气鳄鱼。为了纪念他们时隔三年重返音乐节，他们介绍了 2016 年《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-catfish-and-the-bottlemen-16481-305848#:~:text=%E2%80%9CI%20call%20people%20like%20%5Ba,about%20being%20anything%20more%20than">The Ride</a> 》中的“7”并说道：“你认识那个吗？”</p><p>查看下面的完整歌单。</p></div><div><h3> <strong>2024 年 Catfish 和 Bottlemen 阅读节曲目列表为：</strong></h3></div><div> <strong>“远射”</strong><br /> <strong>“凯瑟琳”</strong><br /> <strong>“声音检查”</strong><br /> <strong>“奶嘴”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;两次&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“辐射”（带有立体声音响“调酒师与小偷”的片段）</strong><br /> <strong>“2全部”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;想家&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;兰戈&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;外部&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;波动&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>‘7’</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;茧&#39;</strong> </div><div><figure id="attachment_3617969" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617969" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3617969" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Catfish@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Catfish 和 The Bottlemen 现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Catfish@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Catfish@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Catfish@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Catfish@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Catfish@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Catfish@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3617969" class="wp-caption-text"> Catfish 和 The Bottlemen 进行现场表演。图片来源：乔治娜·赫德菲尔德</figcaption></figure></div><div><p>Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen 宣布携复出单曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-the-bottlemen-share-comeback-single-showtime-and-announce-more-uk-headline-shows-3591486">Showtime</a> 》回归，该乐队此前曾在二月份在其社交媒体频道上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-post-clip-of-first-new-music-in-five-years-3589012">发布了一段 6 秒的曲目片段来调侃这首</a>歌曲。乐队还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-the-bottlemen-announce-7-inch-and-merch-for-new-single-showtime-back-to-the-graft-again-3590146">发布了预购的 7 英寸白色黑胶唱片《Showtime》以及新商品</a>。</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-the-bottlemen-release-rare-bonus-track-asa-from-the-balcony-10th-anniversary-reissue-3776175">乐队分享了即将发行的《The Balcony》十周年纪念版的附赠曲目《ASA》。</a>该曲目最初于 2013 年作为《Rango》的 B 面发行。</p><p>这支威尔士乐队正准备纪念他们开创性的首张专辑发行十周年。再版将于 9 月 16 日发售 - 请<a href="https://catb.lnk.to/TB10collectionWE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订。</p><p>除了《ASA》之外，《The Balcony》及其十周年再版也将收录<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-22-1222666">Ewan McGregor 翻唱的《Hourglass》</a> 、《Rango》（单曲版）和其他三首额外曲目。</p><p>此外，还将推出限量版7英寸单曲盒装，仅限购买2,000张。</p><p>他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-announce-first-sadium-shows-in-england-and-wales-for-summer-2025-3784801">还宣布了他们的首次体育场巡演</a>，将于 2025 年 8 月开始。门票现已发售，您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fcatfish-and-the-bottlemen-tickets%2Fartist%2F5121447" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024"><i>请返回 NME，</i></a><i>了解雷丁和利兹 2024 年的最新新闻、评论、采访、照片等。</i></p></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-went-down-at-catfish-the-bottlemens-reading-2024-performance-3787107">这篇文章《Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen 2024 年雷丁演出》中发生的事情</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Rough Trade“评估机会”建立新店https://www.nme.com/news/music/rough-trade-assessing-opportunities-to-build-new-stores-3787098?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=rough-trade-assessing-opportunities-to-build-新店Alex RigottiSun, 25 Aug 2024 20:50:49 +0000 Music NewsNewsVinyl https://www.nme.com/?p=3787098 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Rough_Trade.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="粗加工贸易重新开放" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Rough_Trade.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Rough_Trade-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Rough_Trade-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Rough_Trade-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Rough_Trade-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Rough_Trade-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这家唱片连锁店今年在利物浦开设了英国最大的商店</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rough-trade-assessing-opportunities-to-build-new-stores-3787098">Rough Trade 后“评估建立新店的机会”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Rough_Trade.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="粗加工贸易重新开放" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Rough_Trade.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Rough_Trade-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Rough_Trade-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Rough_Trade-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Rough_Trade-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Rough_Trade-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，随着黑胶唱片和 CD 销量的大幅增长，Rough Trade 正在“评估机会”建立更多商店。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/opinion/cd-revival-2022-punk-vinyl-cassette-3155194">CD 复兴？它可能会成为最朋克的音乐格式</a></li></ul><p>董事总经理劳伦斯·蒙哥马利在一次新的采访中告诉<em><a href="https://www.musicweek.com/labels/read/rough-trade-eyes-further-expansion-amid-resurgence-of-physical-sales/090346">《音乐周刊》</a></em> ，该连锁店目前在英国有六家商店，在美国有一家，正在寻求开设更多商店，特别是在伦敦。</p><p>蒙哥马利说：“我们始终关注英国的机会，但我们尊重全国各地优秀的独立商店，因此我们在寻找机会时非常具体。”他还补充说，该连锁店正在“评估伦敦的一些机会，我们在那里拥有强大的团队和运营机构。”</p><p>在此之前，黑胶唱片行业出现了巨大的复苏，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/number-of-uk-independent-record-shops-hits-10-year-high-3597354">独立黑胶唱片商店的数量在今年 3 月创下了 10 年来的新高</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vinyl-outsells-cd-first-time-35-years-3378006">黑胶唱片销量在 2023 年 35 年来首次超过 CD</a> 。</p><p>蒙哥马利告诉<em>《音乐周刊》</em> ：“截至 2024 年，我们的唱片和 CD 销量是五年前的两倍多。” “只要唱片公司和艺术家继续重视像我们这样的独立唱片店所提供的作用，我们相信这种增长就能持续下去。”</p><p>最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rough-trade-to-open-biggest-uk-store-in-liverpool-3565123">Rough Trade 去年 1 月在利物浦开设了他们最大的英国商店</a>，蒙哥马利称人们对这家商店的最初反应“非常积极”。 “每次我们开店时，我们都会承担起为当地社区服务的责任，而利物浦在音乐文化方面有着悠久的历史和现在。” </p><figure id="attachment_3775272" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3775272" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3775272" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="2023 年 12 月 28 日，一位顾客在牛津街的 HMV 商店里浏览黑胶唱片架。图片来源：Peter Nicholls/Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3775272" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年 12 月 28 日，一位顾客在牛津街的 HMV 商店里浏览黑胶唱片架。图片来源：Peter Nicholls/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “我们的下一步是提高现场演出的数量和质量，”蒙哥马利在谈到利物浦场地时补充道。 “我们决定加大对现场场地的投资——它可容纳 300 人，制作质量高，而且看起来很棒。为了使我们的模式发挥作用，拥有零售和场馆的双重目的非常重要，而利物浦是我们在装修能力和质量方面做得最雄心勃勃的。”</p><p>最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/social-media-reacts-to-rough-trades-ill-advised-vinyl-selling-scheme-genuinely-insulting-3780626">Rough Trade 因“不明智”的黑胶唱片销售计划而受到批评</a>。</p><p> 8 月，唱片店宣布该计划将允许人们用“二手唱片与 FlipVinyl 交换现金”，这家标志性唱片店在其网站上将这家公司描述为“德国增长最快的二手黑胶唱片买家，彻底改变了在线销售黑胶唱片的方式”。</p><p>然而，人们很快发现该公司为稀有唱片提供极其低廉的价格，一位用户仅以 9 英镑购买了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-bowie">大卫·鲍伊</a>的《五年》黑胶唱片套装。</p><p>作为回应，Rough Trade <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rough-trade-suspend-much-criticised-vinyl-selling-scheme-were-very-sorry-3780671">发布了一份声明，对该计划表示歉意</a>，称他们“对这个错误感到非常抱歉”。</p><p> “根据许多客户的反馈，很明显我们做出了错误的假设，人们认为这项服务不合适，并认为我们在牟取暴利。”</p><p>声明继续说道：“这不是我们的本意，但我们理解并理解这些批评，并承担全部责任。” “因此，我们将暂停服务，以便有时间重新评估。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rough-trade-assessing-opportunities-to-build-new-stores-3787098">Rough Trade 后“评估建立新店的机会”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
